  "Description": {
    "English": "Meters and meters of high capacity <span class=\"name name-fuel\">carbon nanotubes</span>.<br><br>Their high tensile strength and mild conductivity make these a key component in many <span class=\"name name-technology\">advanced technologies</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "特长的高容量<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳纳米管</span>。<br><br>它的高抗拉强度和温和的导电性使它成为许多<span class=\"name name-technology\">先进技术</span>的关键部件。",
    "TencentChinese": "特长的高容量<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳纳米管</span>。<br><br>它的高抗拉强度和温和的导电性使它成为许多<span class=\"name name-technology\">先进技术</span>的关键部件。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "數公尺長的高容量<span class=\"name name-fuel\">奈米碳管</span>。<br><br>抗張強度高、輕微導電，許多<span class=\"name name-technology\">先進科技</span>都少不了這項元件。"
  },
